				<img src="/images/SAM_0560.jpg" class="img-responsive" id="img-about">
			</div>
			<div class="col-md-8 col-xs-12">
				<p><strong>CARLOS J. PEREZ</strong> is a gifted ceramicist, painter, and illustrator. He draws his inspiration from comics, mythological figures, and Latin culture. Possessing a great attention to detail his work displays traces of his formative years spent growing up in Puerto Rico. Carlos is enrolled in the Teaching Artist Program at Visionaries + Voices, and has gained much experience teaching his style of artwork to students in Greater Cincinnati.</p>
				<break>
				<p>Carlos was born with Autism, a neurological disorder, but this condition has never stopped him.  Since an early age he has demonstrated a unique artistic ability. Before starting a project Carlos does extensive research. All his sculptures are unique and many have been sold as commissioned pieces. Overcoming his condition everyday, Carlos works hard to improve himself as an artist and as a person.</p>
				<break>
				<p><strong>You can support Carlos by purchasing his art.</strong> You can get in touch with him through email or Facebook. Unfortunately we cannot take credit card payments online, but we can settle a payment method through bank deposit or money gram, and after receiving your payment we will ship your order by way of your preferred mailing provider.</p>
			</div>
